		<div class="courseListDescription">This course is based on the premise that the only way to learn how to direct actors is to learn about acting. Students participate in workshop acting exercises, improvisations and discussions on the acting process as it relates to the rehearsal and shooting of dramatic films, from the point of view of actors and directors.</div>
	
	
