		<div class="courseListDescription">This studio course is designed for those with a special interest in writing for film or television, and builds upon skills learned in MPF324-Writing for Film. The course deals with all the stages of dramatic screenwriting from conception and development through to outline and the writing of completed scenes, with a particular focus on developing rich character biographies and the outline and treatment for a short screenplay.</div>
	
	
