		<div class="courseListDescription">This course is an investigation of uses of the human figure in traditional fine arts and contemporary media. This studio course will explore the representation of the figure in two- and three-dimensional design contexts as well as in time-based and digital forms. Participants will have the opportunity to combine studio work with theoretical and historical studies.</div>
	
	
