    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/media-studies/NPF/505.html" title="NPF 505 - Independent Cinema" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">NPF 505</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Independent Cinema</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">The course considers a range of practices that take place outside the framework of support offered by the major cinematic institutions - practices that are shaped by the creative drive of individual filmmakers, the so-called "personal film." Readings will include manifestos, letters and documents generated by the filmmakers who are the principal subjects of study.</div>
	
	
