		<div class="courseListDescription">This course provides a survey and overview of new and evolving media forms. Students will be encouraged to apply innovative ideas, techniques and/or approaches studied in this course to their own visual productions. A range of suggested topics will be presented in class and developed via individual research and investigation.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Lecture: 3 hrs. </span></div>
	
	
