    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/media-studies/NPF/554.html" title="NPF 554 - Advanced Topics in Contemporary Art" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">NPF 554</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Advanced Topics in Contemporary Art</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This course examines relationships among a broad range of media and art practices in the second half of the twentieth century. It explores the theory and practice of selected post-modern art movements in depth, and may focus on one or more of the following: minimalism, pop art, conceptualism, performance art, earthworks, arte povera, photo-realism, neo-expressionism and video and new media practices.</div>
	
	
