		<div class="courseListDescription">This course will consider the influential role of design within film, photography and digital media from a theoretical perspective. Through presentations and class discussions the design process will be reviewed. We will examine a process that begins with design thinking and leads to design implementation, where concepts are transformed into visual realities for particular audiences and to meet communication goals.</div>
	
	
